%% Data Flow Diagram: Model Metadata Collection
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant CICD as CI/CD Pipeline<br/>(Konflux/Tekton)
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>Go CLI
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as OCI Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>data/*.yaml
    participant Build as Container Build<br/>Dockerfile.konflux
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over CICD,Quay: Flow 1: Model Metadata Extraction Pipeline (Build-Time)

    CICD->>Extractor: Invoke model-extractor CLI
    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections<br/>GET /api/models/{id}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth (public)
    HF-->>Extractor: Model collections, details,<br/>READMEs, tags, licenses
    Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests<br/>GET /v2/{repo}/blobs<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    Registry-->>Extractor: Image manifests, layers,<br/>model card content, config blobs
    Note over Extractor: Parse YAML frontmatter<br/>Enrich metadata<br/>Merge & deduplicate
    Extractor->>FS: Write models-catalog.yaml<br/>validated-models-catalog.yaml<br/>other-models-catalog.yaml<br/>+ index files
    FS-->>Build: COPY data/*.yaml /app/data/
    Build->>Quay: Push container image<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Registry Auth

    Note over CICD,Quay: Flow 2: Catalog Data Consumption (Runtime)

    participant Operator as RHOAI Operator
    participant InitC as Init Container<br/>odh-model-metadata-collection
    participant Volume as Shared Volume
    participant MR as Model Registry
    participant Dash as RHOAI Dashboard

    Operator->>InitC: Start init container
    InitC->>Volume: Copy /app/data/*.yaml<br/>to shared volume
    MR->>Volume: Read models-catalog.yaml<br/>File I/O
    Dash->>Volume: Read catalog data<br/>File I/O
    Note over MR,Dash: Model discovery and<br/>user-facing browsing
